wiki.summary: On "Never Stop," the second track on Ian's debut mixtape “Valedictorian”, embodies a powerful message of resilience and self-empowerment. The snippet of this track was first previewed on April 17, 2024, on Ian’s Instagram and was released on May 17, 2024 on Ian’s debut mixtape Valedictorian. The song quickly gained traction, particularly within the TikTok community, where its catchy rhythm and relatable themes resonated with listeners. Read more on Last.fm.
